{
  "texts": [
    "This gap in application presents a unique opportunity to revolutionize the way software is developed.",
    "In this research preview, we present an initial attempt to use LLMs to assist software engineers by progressively refining use cases to functional requirements, design models, test cases, and eventually implementation code.Our work is built on two assumptions.",
    "First, detailed requirements are provided to the LLMs as input.",
    "Second, software engineers' collaboration with LLMs is critical.LLMs need detailed requirements as input.",
    "The recent hype in generative AI makes people have unrealistic expectations for LLMs."
  ]
}